  "description": [
    "1 if a 4 UP AND OVER Travis Doerring of Newington High Track Team crosses bar at 5 ft 5 inches to cop fourth place in recent State Class B Invitational Indoor Tracks Meet held at Yale University Student OneActors Creditably Staged in Sound Comedy Trio The Newington High Jun iorSenior and Sophomore Dramatic Clubs presented An Evening of Comedy at the high school audit orium last week The Evening consisted of three oneact plays which were presented with the Sophomore Club play The Ugly Duckling starting off and The Flat tering Word and The Tragedy of Romeo and Jul iet following The Ugly Duckling concerns the attempts of a king and queen to marry off their daughter and the in trigues involved Gary Jones as the king and John Hannon as the chancellor performed exceptionally well Other cast members were Geraldine DAngelo as Dulcibelle Jacqueline Coe as the queen Larry Brophy as Carlo Judy Wol finger as the Princess and lames Cuart as the Prince In The Flattering Word Walter Jackson did a fine job of portraying the role of Eugene Tesh an actor and Patricia Phenix who played Mrs Zooker a Church Worker turned in a creditable performance"
